element.text: NO, YOU ARE NOT SLOW, THE CITY IS LARGE. YOU DIDNT REALLY EXPECT TO WALK ACROSS AN ENTIRE CITY IN 3 STEPS DID YOU? IT PROBABLY TOOK YOU QUITE A WHILE TO FIND THIS, OR MAYBE IT DIDNT. EITHER WAY I HOPE YOU ENJOYED YOUR TIME IN THIS BEAUTIFUL CITY. IT DOES HAS A NAME BUT I WONT TELL YOU WHAT IT IS
